description: Add the skill to your echo and then just say 'Alexa, ask Nebraska facts for a fact'. You can ask for "a fact", "something", "trivia", or just say "Alexa, ask Nebraska Facts to tell me something". You will get a random fact about Nebraska in return.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Nebraska facts for a fact.
Alexa, ask Nebraska facts for a nebraska fact.
Alexa, ask Nebraska facts to tell me something.
name: nebraska facts
shortDescription: A skill to get random facts about Nebraska.
